Question: Find the VCE for the circuit shown in 
<image 1>. Neglect VBE
Answer: 3.75
Explanation: …IE = [(VEE) / 
(RE)] = [(5 V) / (4 k-ohm)] = 
1.25 mA; VCE = VCC - IERL = 
10 V - (1.25 mA) 5 k-ohm; 
VCE = 10 V - 6.25 V = 3.75 V
